title: AWS ELB: Backend Errors
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the connection errors between AWS/ELB and
 the servers occur when ELB attempts to connect to a backend.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {{Amazon Web Services (AWS)}}.

 No default levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} are set.
 These are configurable.

inventory:
 One service is created if all required metrics (BackendConnectionErrors) are given.
